                        <row>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>1.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Off</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Remove Speedo/Tach module and make sure the odometer is plugged securely into the
                                    module circuit board.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para></para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Good connection?</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Go to next step.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Connect and retest.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>2.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Off</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Disconnect odometer lead and momentarily apply 12V across the odometer leads. Each
                                    time power is applied, the odometer should increment.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para></para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Odometer increments?</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Replace Speedo/ Tach module.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Replace odometer.</para>
                            </entry>
